title: Episode 136: Website Hackings, Muslim Prayers, and Oxford Press!
description: French websites hacked and comedians arrested! Muslim prayers at Duke University and no pigs at Oxford Press! It’s post-Charlie Hebdo madness, dear listeners! Plus, the gang responds to your mail… all on the podcast this week!
